I really like what she said about which of the bill should be put first when it comes to marijuana. Help those in Prison over the Banks. But pass them both.  Yes, her understand of the historical affect of American institutions and polices from slavery to redlining is correct but there are poor, working class, middle class, and wealth black, brown, asian and white folk. To continuously refer to black and brown folks as an automatically  a lower class is an example of the hidden racism in the ideology of the Left. Yes racism is very real. It is not over. It has just gotten more sophisticated. I still feel it is more important to help poor, working class, and middle class white people that we have more in common than billionaire WASP that are destroying the plant and pitting Americans against other Americans.
